    "long_instructions": "### Ramona's Song\r\nRamona is in a groove and really wants to use the Reggaeton Beat and the Groovy Beat Two throughout his song. \r\n\r\nShe wants you to add bass, leads, and effects to make her song come to life. \r\n\r\nHer only requirements are: \r\n- The Reggaeton Beat starts the song off for 6 measures\r\n- Then the Groovy Beat Two plays for 4 measures\r\n- Last, the Reggaeton Beat comes back for 2 measures\r\n",
